<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss version="2.0"><channel><title>Moments · 叶枫影</title><description>生活的片段。照片、音乐与随笔。</description><link>https://moments.leafvmaple.com/</link><language>zh-CN</language><item><title>为什么是听枫阁</title><link>https://moments.leafvmaple.com/posts/start-here/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://moments.leafvmaple.com/posts/start-here/</guid><description>一个写给几年后翻回来还能记得当时是什么样子的地方。不追阅读，不追热度。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>随笔</category></item><item><title>庚子年正月，东京一日</title><link>https://moments.leafvmaple.com/posts/tokyo/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://moments.leafvmaple.com/posts/tokyo/</guid><description>新干线把 500 公里压成两个半小时；秋叶原把所有二次元粉丝想要的东西压成八层楼。从大阪到东京，是从「慢板」走到「极致细分」。</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2020 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>旅行</category><category>东京</category><category>日本</category></item><item><title>庚子年正月，京都一日</title><link>https://moments.leafvmaple.com/posts/kyoto-winter/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://moments.leafvmaple.com/posts/kyoto-winter/</guid><description>半天岚山，半天伏见。早上的灰、下午的红，被一条 JR 京都线连成一句话。</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2020 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>旅行</category><category>京都</category><category>日本</category></item><item><title>庚子年正月，大阪一日</title><link>https://moments.leafvmaple.com/posts/osaka/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://moments.leafvmaple.com/posts/osaka/</guid><description>一座一千多万人的都会，正月里却像一首慢板。护城河的水是绿的，天守阁的金箔是新的，松屋的牛丼是热的 —— 大阪不动声色地把「古」和「今」叠在一起。</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2020 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category>旅行</category><category>大阪</category><category>日本</category></item></channel></rss>